[01:36.87]Many adoptees want to search for them,
[01:40.11]but others do not.
[01:42.85]The decision to search for birth parents is a difficult one to make.
[01:46.77]Most adoptees have mixed feelings about finding their biological parents.
[01:52.76]Even though adoptees do not know about their natural parents,
[01:59.43]they do know that their adoptive parents want them,
[02:02.47]love them and will care for them.

